name: Verify Admin Navigate to Batch Page successfully
fullName: tests/features/04_Batch.feature#Verify Admin Navigate to Batch Page successfully

steps.name: the user is in Login Page
the user enters the username "playwrightuser@gmail.com" and "Playwright@1234"
the user navigates to the Dashboard page and get the title for verification
Given Admin is on the Dashboard page
When Admin clicks Batch on the Menu from the header
When Admin clicks on "Add New batch" under the "batch" menu bar
When Admin enters "DataAnalyst", "","Developer","Active","12" and click save button
Then Admin should a message "Batch Name is required."
